<section xml:id="section-structure">
  <title>Course Structure: Videos, Notes, Activities</title>
  <p>
    This course is structure around videos and class activites. For
    most classes, there is a video to watch before class and an
    activity to do during class based on that video. 
  </p>
  <p>
    These notes are meant to accompany the videos. They serve as a
    record and reference for the material in the videos. They also
    include expansion on some topics<mdash/>detail that I wasn't
    able to fit into the run time of the videos. Finally, they also
    include some review material for your convenience. 
  </p>
</section>
